><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Warrior Upgrades...</span><hr size=1> This topic was discussed in a few other threads.  Many players, most warriors, and some who can just &quot;see it&quot; think we seriously need an upgrade.  I'm one of those who feels that we are vastly underpowered.  From no special skills to save our own asses in a pinch, to lower damage output than the hybrids no counting spells.  To the new block mods on shields, the AC cap, and a constantly shrinking HP advantage.  Anyone who plays a warrior knows all about this, anyone who disagrees in my opinion simply has not played a warrior long enough to understand, or is completely UBER and doesn't realize that not all of us visit VT daily.  As far as Velious Quest armors go, it makes us warriors fall well below par.  <br>
<br>
Many people feel differently than the above, that is your choice.  What I want to discuss in this thread (for those who agree with me) is what the hell can we do to improve our situation?  Petition?  Write e-mails?  Post to some EQ message board?  Hand written letters for crying out loud?  <br>
<br>
<br>
First warriors need to decide what we want other than Gimick_upgrade_001.  Please also post ideas for potential upgrade that isn't overpowering or chessy, like giving us mana.  If you don't think we need an upgrade, this is not the place to post or flame, kindly take your thoughts to the tons of other boards where they are arguing about this topic.  This is a place to discuss what we want and how are we going to get it...<br>
<br>
