<br>
However, it also might be nice if they gave us a more useful taunt ability.  Perhaps just fleshing out the existing taunt and making it actually add a small amount of hate instead of just temporarily moving us to the top of the hate list, only to be instantly knocked off again by the monk/rogue/ranger/wizard/cleric of the group.<br>
<br>
Honestly, if they'd just throw us a bone in these two categories, I'd probably shut up, hehe.<br>
